data.description: This 2 bed/2 bath manufactured home is within 0.5 miles of Lake Oroville. It was manufactured in 1990 and has been well-cared for. The home boasts a pellet stove to keep you warm in the winter and central air conditioning to keep you cool in the summer. There are also 2 storage sheds on the property for all your tools and toys as well as a covered carport.
